  "text": "The blood flow values of the femoral and the tibial condyles obtained in this study are in accordance with earlier reports [CITATION_1] . We have confirmed the data of Okubo et al. [CITATION_2] , who also reported higher blood flow values in the tibial as compared to the femoral condyles. In contrast to McGrory et al. [CITATION_3] , we did not observe changes of RBBF over a period of 60 min.",
